	- Okay, but why am I working a 9 to 5?
		Cecil: Didn't you pay attention in the orientation? This place only runs because miserable losers like us keep it going. They feed off our misery and despair. They'll tell you its about functionality and efficiency and sales, whatever that means to literal HELL. Don't fall for that propaganda bullshit. The machine needs us and it can't get enough of our sad pitiful existences stuck here forever.
		- What do we do? Can we get out of here?
			Cecil: Get out of here? HAHAHA. Wake up and look around. There isn't anywhere to go. This is eternity.
